name: DinosaurMatch
0:
”Alexa, play Dinosaur Match”
”yes”
”can you tell me more”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dinosaur match
des:
Have you ever wanted to go back in time and study dinosaurs? What were the differences between them? Some were carnivores and some were herbivores. Some were big and some were huge. Answer a few simple questions, and this skill will pick which dinosaur most suits you!

To learn more about these dinosaurs, just say "Can you tell me more" after the sorting process is complete, and a brief description will be read about the specific species.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
